entry.title: Scikit-Learn House Price AI
entry.content:
Goals: Get accustomed to Jupyter Notebooks, Scikit-Learn, and simple regression AI modeling. Learn concepts such as normalization, imputation, and the foundations of CRISP-DM.
Results: Model with an r2 of 0.9999968, but is not general to any house due to location data being factored into the model.
